high_descs: Turn left, move forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Pick up the cup in the sink, to the left of the sponge.
Turn left, move forward, then turn right to approach the microwave.
Warm up the cup in the microwave.
Turn around, go forward, then go left to return to the fridge
Put the cup in the fridge, in front of the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the kitchen sink.
Remove the gold wine glass from inside the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave, on your right,  at the end of the counter.
Place the wine glass in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the wine glass from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter, then make a left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the wine glass in front of the tomato, on the top shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm wine glass in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn to the left, then left again to find the sink.
Pick up the glass from the left side of the sink.
Carry the glass and take a few steps left to the microwave.
Place the glass inside the microwave, then take the glass out and shut the door.
Carry the glass and turn around, then left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the glass inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat and then chill a glass.
